While using Our Application, We **do not request, collect, or require** any personally identifiable information (such as your name, email address, phone number, or precise location data).
**Usage and Feature Data**
Our Application functions entirely locally on your Device.
 * **Calendar Calculations:** All conversions between Bangla San (with seasons/Ritu), English, and Hijri calendars, including your manual Hijri date adjustments, are calculated strictly on your Device.
 * **Home Screen Widgets & Trackers:** The data you input into the Countdown & Age Tracker and the configurations for the "Clock Bangla" and "Countdown" widgets remain on your Device.
